Comment:
Hey Mark I'm sure that you're getting a lot of tips from practically everyone but I just wanted to share some things that I've learned that may help a bit. 

Edit: this is just speculation but you're obviously welcome to try it but Lucas may crouch when he's coming down the hallway to avoid the motion sensors and while he's picking the lock so if you go with the motion sensors next time put them at knee length if that's possible. 
He also comes from both ends of the hallway so put them on either side of your door so he can't avoid triggering at least one of them. 

Also, the trafficking/pedo sights are heavily monitored by police and it will increase your chance of police tracking you.

Edit: I was told that the wiki 3 link is gotten after the rule of three puzzle (not the second lol) You need to get to wiki 3 in order to get all of the keys and win. :)

The dollmaker's website can sometimes contain a key but what I've seen so far hasn't said that it's not necessary to go to his site (and trigger the quest) to complete the game unless the key happens to be on that website. It's all randomized.

I'm sorry if you knew all of this already and this isn't helpful but I know you really want to beat the game so I thought I would try to help. I'm super excited to see you win after you've put so much effort into this! Good luck!! :)
